metadata.name: Principles (Superbloom Mix)
metadata.description:
① → MAKE MORE IMAGINATION.

② → LISTEN TO THE CREATORS, ENABLE THE CREATORS.

③ → PRIORITIZE RESONANCE OVER RELEVANCE.

④ → FOLLOW THE FEELING, THEN MAKE IT MAKE SENSE.

⑤ → MOMENTUM IS EVERYTHING, SO START NOW.

⑥ → REVEAL THE VALUE AND HELP IT HIT.

⑦ → COMBINE DESIGN, ENGINEERING AND MYTH.

⑧ → MAKE IT FEEL LIKE IT WAS ALWAYS THERE.

⑨ → DON’T RUSH DURING FULL MOONS AND RETROGRADES.

⑩ → OPEN HEARTS, OPEN MINDS, OPEN SOURCE.

⑪ → ANGEL NUMBERS, LIGHT MODE, FULL SEND.
